Package ohos.data.distributed.common

Class FieldNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.distributed.common.FieldNode

  • public class FieldNode
extends Object
    Represents a node of a Schema instance.

    Through the Schema instance, you can define the fields contained in the values stored in a database.

    A FieldNode of the Schema instance is either a leaf or a non-leaf node.

    The leaf node must have a value; the non-leaf node must have a child FieldNode.

    Since:
    3
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_DISTRIBUTEDDATAMGR
